法国人[[阿尔塞纳·温格|阿尔塞纳·温格]]率[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿森纳]]在他完整执教的第一个赛季，即[[1997–98賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|1997-98赛季]]领先曼联12分夺冠，使他成为了第一个获得该奖的非英国人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/1281890.stm |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |work=BBC Sport |date=2001-05-14 |accessdate=2012-01-14 |title=Top bosses made to wait |archive-date=2016-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113025325/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/1281890.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.examiner.ie/sport/soccer/angry-fergie-comes-out-fighting-147343.html|work=[[Irish_Examiner|Irish Examiner]]|date=2011-03-05|accessdate=2012-01-14|last=Stone|first=Simon|title=Angry Fergie comes out fighting|archive-date=2020-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200426065942/https://www.irishexaminer.com/sport/soccer/angry-fergie-comes-out-fighting-147343.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[1998–99賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|1998-99赛季]]则是曼联的[[三冠王_(足球)|三冠王]]（[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英超]]、[[英格蘭足總盃|足总杯]]、[[欧洲冠军联赛|欧冠]]）赛季，弗格森再次获得最佳教练<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/football/fa_carling_premiership/345385.stm|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation|work=BBC News|date=1999-05-17|accessdate=2012-01-13|title=Fergie is top boss|archive-date=2016-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113025327/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/football/fa_carling_premiership/345385.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[1999–2000賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|1999-00赛季]]曼联领先阿森纳18分夺冠，再次成功卫冕<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/football/fa_carling_premiership/749585.stm|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation|work=BBC News|date=2000-05-15|accessdate=2012-01-13|title=Fergie wins manager award|archive-date=2016-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113025327/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/football/fa_carling_premiership/749585.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[2000–01賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2000-01赛季]]，{{link-en|乔治·伯利|George Burley}}带领[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|伊普斯维奇]]以[[升降班制度|升班马]]的身份取得了英超第五，晋级[[欧足联欧洲联赛|欧洲联盟杯]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/1338654.stm|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation|work=BBC News|date=2001-05-19|accessdate=2012-01-14|title=Derby dent Ipswich hopes|archive-date=2016-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113025328/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/1338654.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他成为了第一个没有夺冠而获得该奖的主教练<ref name="Burley"/>；他击败了率曼联完成三连冠的弗格森，以及带[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]夺得[[足總盃|足总杯]]、[[聯賽盃|联赛杯]]、[[欧足联欧洲联赛|欧洲联盟杯]]冠军以及英超第三的[[热拉尔·乌利耶|热拉尔·乌利耶]]<ref name="Burley"/>。[[2001–02賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2001-02赛季]]，温格率领阿森纳取得十三连胜，再次夺冠，以此获得了赛季最佳主教练奖<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/arsenal/1985879.stm|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation|work=BBC Sport|date=2002-05-13|accessdate=2012-01-13|title=Wenger wins double honours|archive-date=2016-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113025328/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/arsenal/1985879.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。弗格森则在[[2002–03賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2002-03赛季]]以再次带曼联夺冠的成绩获奖<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2003/may/13/newsstory.sport9|work=[[guardian.co.uk|guardian.co.uk]]|publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]]|date=2003-05-13|accessdate=2012-01-14|title=Moyes manager of the year|archive-date=2009-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090816235742/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2003/may/13/newsstory.sport9|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[2003–04賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2003-04赛季]]则是阿森纳的不败赛季，温格以此前无古人的伟绩获得了赛季最佳主教练，并收到了评奖小组的高度赞扬<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11670_2299422,00.html|work=Sky Sports|accessdate=2012-01-14|title=Gunners duo land more awards|first=James|last=Pearson|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310083148/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11670_2299422,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

狂人[[若泽·穆里尼奥|若泽·穆里尼奥]]在[[2004–05賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2004-05赛季]]率领切尔西夺得了50年以来的第一个联赛冠军<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/chelsea/4544479.stm|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation|work=BBC Sport|date=2005-05-13|accessdate=2012-01-14|title=Chelsea trio scoop season awards|archive-date=2016-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113025329/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/chelsea/4544479.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，切尔西单赛季得95分，仅失15球，均创造了英超联赛的新纪录<ref>{{Cite web|title=Wenger: 78–80 points enough for title|url=http://www.espnstar.com/football/premier-league/news/detail/item546550/Wenger:-78-80-points-enough-for-title/|accessdate=2012-01-23|author=|date=|format=|publisher=[[ESPN_STAR_Sports|ESPN STAR Sports]]|language=|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120730001614/http://www.espnstar.com/football/premier-league/news/detail/item546550/Wenger:-78-80-points-enough-for-title/|archivedate=2012-07-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Chelsea 2004–2005 : English Premier League Table|url=http://www.statto.com/football/teams/chelsea/2004-2005/table|accessdate=2012-01-25|author=|date=|format=|work=Statto.com|publisher=|language=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206093752/http://www.statto.com/football/teams/chelsea/2004-2005/table|archivedate=2013-12-06}}</ref>。下一个赛季，穆里尼奥再次率队夺冠，使得他连续两个赛季获得赛季最佳主教练<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/chelsea/4752527.stm|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation|work=BBC Sport|date=2006-05-08|accessdate=2012-01-13|title=Mourinho scoops managerial award|archive-date=2016-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113025627/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/chelsea/4752527.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006-07赛季，弗格森带曼联夺回了阔别四年的联赛冠军，并再次完成英超三连冠，自己也连续三次获得最佳主教练<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sportinglife.com/football/nat1teams/sunderland/news/story_get.cgi?STORY_NAME=soccer/07/05/16/manual_105751.html&TEAMHD=sunderland&DIV=nat1&TEAM=SUNDERLAND&RH=Sunderland&PREV_SEASON=&BID=|work=[[Sporting_Life_(British_newspaper)|sportinglife.com]]|publisher=[[365_Media_Group|365 Media Group]]|accessdate=2012-01-14|title=Keane picks up managerial gong|archive-date=2020-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200426065948/https://www.sportinglife.com/football/nat1teams/sunderland/news/story_get.cgi?STORY_NAME=soccer%2F07%2F05%2F16%2Fmanual_105751.html&TEAMHD=sunderland&DIV=nat1&TEAM=SUNDERLAND&RH=Sunderland&PREV_SEASON=&BID=|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Eight"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8069391.stm|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation|work=BBC Sport|date=2009-05-28|accessdate=2012-01-14|title=Moyes wins record third LMA award|archive-date=2016-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113025627/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8069391.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[2009–10賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2009-10赛季]]，[[哈里·雷德克纳普|哈里·雷德克纳普]]执教的[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|托特纳姆热刺]]二十年来首次杀入英超前四，获得最佳主教练，当赛季的冠军则是[[卡洛·安切洛蒂|卡洛·安切洛蒂]]执教的切尔西<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.irishexaminer.com/sport/soccer/redknapp-is-named-manager-of-the-season-119258.html|work=[[Irish_Examiner|Irish Examiner]]|date=2010-05-08|accessdate=2020-08-25|title=Redknapp is named manager of the season|archive-date=2010-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100511214745/http://www.irishexaminer.com/sport/soccer/redknapp-is-named-manager-of-the-season-119258.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年5月，弗格森以冠军主教练的身份，接受了自己的第十个赛季最佳主教练奖<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/13479964.stm|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation|work=BBC Sport|date=2011-05-20|accessdate=2012-01-14|title=Sir Alex Ferguson and Nemanja Vidic win season awards|archive-date=2020-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200426065936/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/13479964|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[2011–12賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2011-12赛季]]，[[阿兰·帕杜|阿兰·帕杜]]率[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|纽卡斯尔联]]取得英超第五名这一九年以来的最好成绩，因此得奖，当年的冠军是[[羅拔圖·文仙尼|罗伯托·曼奇尼]]执教的[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]<ref name="Pardew" />。2013年5月，弗格森带曼联夺冠，获得赛季最佳主教练，并在该赛季后退休<ref name="ferguson20">{{cite news|language=vi|author=T.Vĩ|title=Alex Ferguson - HLV xuất sắc nhất giải Ngoại hạng Anh năm 2013|url=http://thethao.tuoitre.vn/tin/2013/05/22/cac-mon-khac/alex-ferguson-hlv-xuat-sac-nhat-giai-ngoai-hang-anh-nam-2013/4004.html|accessdate=2014-03-09|newspaper=[[Tuổi_Trẻ|Tuổi Trẻ]]|date=2013-05-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309112640/http://thethao.tuoitre.vn/tin/2013/05/22/cac-mon-khac/alex-ferguson-hlv-xuat-sac-nhat-giai-ngoai-hang-anh-nam-2013/4004.html|archivedate=2014-03-09|work=|publisher=|format=}}</ref>。[[2013–14賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2013-14赛季]]的[[東尼·佩利斯|托尼·普利斯]]，在[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宫]]11轮取4分排名垫底的情况下接手球队，最终获得英超第11名，成为第一个获得该奖的[[威爾斯|威尔士]]主教练，当赛季[[曼努埃尔·佩莱格里尼|曼努埃尔·佩莱格里尼]]带曼城夺冠<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/may/13/luis-suarez-tony-pulis-barclays-awards | work = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | accessdate = 2014-05-13 | date = 2014-05-13 | title = Luis Suárez and Tony Pulis scoop Barclays Premier League season awards | archive-date = 2018-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180928220709/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/may/13/luis-suarez-tony-pulis-barclays-awards | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[2014年至2015年英格蘭足球超級聯賽|2014-15赛季]]，回归切尔西的穆里尼奥率队夺冠，获得赛季最佳主教练<ref name="Mourinho"/>。

[[2015–16賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2015-16赛季]]，[[克劳迪奥·拉涅利|克劳迪奥·拉涅利]]率领上一个赛季勉强保级的[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]神奇夺冠，获得最佳主教练<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Manager profile, Claudio Ranieri|url=http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/clubs/managers/profile.overview.html/claudio-ranieri|accessdate=2016-05-18|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Premier League|language=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160526225826/http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/clubs/managers/profile.overview.html/claudio-ranieri|archivedate=2016-05-26}}</ref>。[[2016年至2017年英格蘭足球超級聯賽|2016-17赛季]]，[[安東尼奧·孔蒂|安东尼奥·孔蒂]]执教的切尔西夺冠，他获得赛季最佳主教练<ref name=":1">{{Cite web |url=https://www.premierleague.com/news/401576 |publisher=Premier League |date=2017-05-23 |accessdate=2017-05-23 |title=Conte named Barclays Manager of the Season |archive-date=2018-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180909025332/https://www.premierleague.com/news/401576 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2017年至2018年英格蘭足球超級聯賽|2017-18赛季]]，[[佩普·瓜迪奥拉|佩普·瓜迪奥拉]]带[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]夺冠，取得100个积分，打进106球，赢球32场，连胜18场，均打破英超联赛记录，成为了第一个获得该奖的西班牙教练<ref name=":2">{{Cite web |url=https://www.premierleague.com/news/690752 |publisher=Premier League |date=2018-05-15 |accessdate=2018-05-16 |title=Guardiola named Barclays Manager of the Season |archive-date=2018-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180516041433/https://www.premierleague.com/news/690752 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。下个赛季，瓜迪奥拉带队有惊无险地夺冠，蝉联赛季最佳主教练<ref name=":2" />。

[[2019年至2020年英格蘭足球超級聯賽|2019-20赛季]]，尤尔根·克洛普率利物浦夺得俱乐部历史上第一个英超冠军，获得最佳主教练奖<ref name=":3">{{Cite web |url=https://www.premierleague.com/news/1750637 |publisher=Premier League |date=2020-08-15 |accessdate=2020-08-15 |title=Klopp earns 2019/20 Barclays Manager of the Season award |archive-date=2020-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815181513/https://www.premierleague.com/news/1750637 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2020年至2021年英格蘭足球超級聯賽|2020-21赛季]]，佩普·瓜迪奥拉率曼城夺冠，第三次获最佳主教练奖<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|title=Guardiola claims Barclays Manager of the Season award|url=https://www.premierleague.com/news/2164972|access-date=2021-06-05|date=2021-06-05|publisher=Premier League}}</ref>。2021-22赛季，尤尔根·克洛普第二次获最佳主教练奖<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|title=Klopp named Barclays Manager of the Season|url= https://www.premierleague.com/news/2621846|access-date=2022-05-24|date=2022-05-24|publisher=Premier League}}</ref>。

